codex
The key correction is that `UiComponentConfig` is not currently a separate per-view or per-component tree object; the header says it extends `UiConfig`, has inherited `UiConfig` defaults, and is still a placeholder for component-specific configuration. I’m keeping the structure and code blocks mostly intact, but tightening claims about ownership, View trees, and generated chain methods.
